## CounterStyleStatic.alphabeticFromUnicodeRange property

Create an alphabetic renderer from a unicode and an alphabet length. The set of symbols for this alphabetic system will be generated by incrementing `originUnicode` with every integer in range \[0, `alphabetLength` - 1\].

https://www.w3.org/TR/css-counter-styles-3/\#alphabetic-system.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
alphabeticFromUnicodeRange: (originUnicode: number, alphabetLength: number) => CounterStyleRenderer;
```
